description: Step inside and be greeted by a freshly painted airy and inviting atmosphere as we welcome you to this charming one-bedroom, one-and-a-half-bathroom condo! The second bedroom has been cleverly opened up to create additional living space, offering flexibility, ample walk-in closet space and versatility to suit your needs. With impact windows throughout, natural light floods the space, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance. This condo boasts newer air conditioning, ensuring your comfort year-round, fresh paint, newer water heater and electrical panel! Situated in a great location, this condo offers easy access to all that the community has to offer. Enjoy a plethora of amenities, from recreational facilities to lush green spaces, perfect for relaxation and outdoor activities. Monthly Fee Includes Cable, Wi-Fi, and Water! Don't miss on the opportunity to make this corner condo your new Florida home!
